collection.description:
ACTUAL OWNER COUNT: 1588 as of 5/14/22 with 96% staked in gameplay.

EtherOrcs Allies: https://opensea.io/collection/etherorcsallies

EtherOrcs Loot: https://opensea.io/collection/etherorcsloot

EtherOrcs Items: https://opensea.io/collection/etherorcs-items

EtherOrcs is a collection of 5050 Orcs ready to pillage the blockchain. With no IPFS or API, these Orcs are the very first game that takes place 100% on-chain. 

Use your Orc to take part in an ever evolving on-chain gaming experience. Pillage for new gear, raid for new allies, battle in the Arena for rewards, and much more. This Horde of Orcs will stand the test of time and live on the blockchain for eternity.

Visit our site to learn more: https://etherorcs.com/
